node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 14, 2021 tagging @thestorytohealing. May be an image of text that says 'let go of anything that does not make you whole -KARLIEMARIE'.

node.text:
If it feels like it's taking something away from you,⠀
let it go 💌⠀
(cr: @thestorytohealing)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 14, 2021 tagging @itswinnita. May be an image of text that says 'don t blame yourself for having no energy to fight other people's battles anymore -winnie nantongo'.

node.text:
Repeat after me:⠀
Other people's problems are not my responsibility ⠀
(cr: @itswinnita)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 14, 2021 tagging @rhiannonjanae_. May be an image of text that says 'you are enough even on your bad days when you yell too loud or cry too soft when you feel if you're going crumble as the walls cave in at your expense as to when your lungs can't catch your breath and your hair tangles as you lay in bed with your unbathed body. you are and will always be enough. -rhiannonjanae'.

Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 14, 2021 tagging @justbelmont. May be a black-and-white image of flower and text that says 'We all want to be great; the world needs us to be good. -jb-'.

node.text:
The perfect reminder by @justbelmont 👣⠀
Tag someone who needs to read this.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 13, 2021 tagging @natalyajohnson_. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'You are loved through your good days. You are loved through your bad days. You are loved through your heavy days. You are loved when you are broken. You are loved when you don't have strength. You are loved when you feel like you can't. You are loved when you don't have the energy. You are loved when you don' know which way to turn. You are loved when you can't figure it out. You are loved when you are weak. You are loved through it all. Natalya Johnson'.

node.text:
Repeat after me: You Are Loved ✨ ⠀
(cr: @natalyajohnson_)
